REPORT ZPRG_SAMPLE_SUB_EXT.
DATA : ou TYPE numc3.
PARAMETERS : l1 TYPE numc3.
PARAMETERS : l2 TYPE numc3.

*PERFORM sum(ZPRG_SAMPLE_SUB_PARA) USING l1 l2 CHANGING ou.
PERFORM sum IN PROGRAM ZPRG_SAMPLE_SUB_PARA USING l1 l2 CHANGING ou IF FOUND.

WRITE ou.
